a big star, lucas scott.

02:02.035 --> 02:03.035
Mm-Hmm.

02:04.836 --> 02:10.036
* so many years apart
i've missed *

02:10.104 --> 02:12.304
You know, hales, with everything
you've been through lately,

02:12.370 --> 02:13.937
I'm sure principal turner
would understand

02:14.003 --> 02:15.471
If you needed a little
more time off.

02:15.538 --> 02:17.971
I think two weeks
of replaying that day

02:18.038 --> 02:19.405
In my head is enough.

02:19.472 --> 02:21.838
It's time for me to get back
to my life.

02:21.905 --> 02:24.839
Besides, it will be nice
to have the distraction.

02:24.905 --> 02:26.939
If you need me,
you know i'm here.

02:27.005 --> 02:28.772
Yeah.

02:28.840 --> 02:30.873
You know what?
Let's cut through shop.

02:31.677 --> 02:33.252
You can cut through shop?

02:33.288 --> 02:34.882
